'''等比例税'''是一种固定[[税率|税率]]的[[稅|税]]，它的[[税率|税率]]不会随着征税部分收入的增加或减少而改变，所以税额与征税部分收入成比例。<ref>Sommerfeld, Ray M., Silvia A. Madeo, Kenneth E. Anderson, Betty R. Jackson (1992), ''Concepts of Taxation'', Dryden Press: Fort Worth, TX</ref>“等比例”描述了这种税对收入或支出的分配效应，特指其税率始终保持一致（随着[[收入|收入]]或[[消费|消费]]变化不会增高或者降低），边际税率始终不变。<ref name="Hyman">Hyman, David M. (1990) ''Public Finance: A Contemporary Application of Theory to Policy'', 3rd, Dryden Press: Chicago, IL</ref><ref name="James">James, Simon (1998) ''A Dictionary of Taxation'', Edgar Elgar Publishing Limited: Northampton, MA</ref>   

